name: punegrocery
overview:
Punegrocery.in is an internet based Supermarket shopping and online grocery store site in Pune, India. Website allows users to purchase products from different categories like grocery & staples, Beverages, Personal Care, Health Care, Household Care, Branded Food, Fruits & Vegetables, Confectionary and Dairy Products.

Easier Supermarket Shopping Shoppers can fill their shopping cart by simply browsing the categories (online shelves), shopping from the Top Offers or using the Find or Quick Shop (shopping list ) function.

A Source of Essential Grocery Information Pungrocery newsletter is a source of essential news, articles, recipes, and product and health information - helping shoppers make informed decisions, improve their shopping experience and get the cheapest, healthiest groceries each week.

Punegrocery provide free grocery home delivery. There is a small home delivery charge for low amount order. Customer can pay their order when it reaches to their home through cash on delivery or they can simply swipe the debit or credit card. All the card swapping devices are provided by reputed banks.
